---

## üìù Code Style Consistency

### Naming Conventions

**Services:**
- Class: `UserService` (PascalCase)
- File: `user.service.ts` (kebab-case)
- Variable: `userService` (camelCase)

**Components:**
- Class: `UserComponent` (PascalCase)
- File: `user.component.ts` (kebab-case)
- Selector: `app-user` (kebab-case)

**Interfaces:**
- Name: `IUserService` or `UserService` (PascalCase)
- File: `user-service.interface.ts` (kebab-case)

### Code Structure

**Always follow existing patterns:**
- Same import order
- Same class structure
- Same method organization
- Same comment style

### Consistency Checklist

- [ ] Matches existing naming conventions
- [ ] Follows existing code structure
- [ ] Uses same import style
- [ ] Matches existing formatting
- [ ] Uses same comment style

